'''Mark Drakeford''' (genys 19 mis Gwynngala 1954 yn [[Karvyrdhin]]) yw politeger a [[Kembra|Gembra]]. Ledyer [[Parti Lavur]] yn Kembra ha’n [[Kynsa Menyster a Gembra]] a-dhia 2018 yw. Ev yw an esel [[Senedh Kembra]] rag [[Kardydh|Kardydh West]] a-dhia 2011.<ref name="CY">[https://gov.wales/rt-hon-mark-drakeford-ms Rt Hon Mark Drakeford MS], ''gov.wales'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), kyrghys 24 mis Ebrel 2022</ref>

A-dhia 2013 dhe 2016, Drakeford o Menyster rag Yeghes ha Servisyow Socyal hag a-dhia 2016 dhe 2018, ev o an Skrifennyas Kabinet rag Arhans yn-dann [[Carwyn Jones]].<ref name=CY /> Pan omdennas Jones yn 2018, Drakeford a veu etholys an ledyer ha Kynsa Menyster, ow fethas [[Vaughan Gething]].<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-46471728 Welsh Labour leadership: Mark Drakeford set to be Wales’ first minister], ''[[BBC]]'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), 6 mis Kevardhu 2018, kyrghys 24 mis Ebrel 2022</ref> Y’n [[Etholans Senedh Kembra 2021|etholans Senedh Kembra yn 2021]], Drakeford ha’n Parti Lavur yn Kembra a gwaynyas 30 esedhi, rann-vrassa y’n Senedh, ha remaynyas avel Kynsa Menyster.<ref>[https://www.itv.com/news/wales/2021-05-07/senedd-election-2021-live-results-for-wales Senedd Election 2021: What are the results in my area?], ''ITV'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), 8 mis Me 2021, kyrghys 24 mis Ebrel 2022</ref>

Drakeford a skoodhyas [[Jeremy Corbyn]] yn an etholans Ledyer Parti Lavur yn 2015.<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-politics-33941446 Mark Drakeford supports Jeremy Corbyn as Labour leader], ''[[BBC]]'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), 14 mis Est 2015, kyrghys 24 mis Ebrel 2022</ref>

